          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joints</text> - add as sets of two(2) with one(1) <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joint</text> at each end of one(1) <text styleclass="Element">Part</text>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><image src="Red-14-6.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joint</text> two <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Points</text> from two <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">parts</text> in <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Mechanism B</text><text styleclass="Image Caption">. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><image src="Red-14-7.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joint -</text> one <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Point</text> in <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Mechanism B,</text> one <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Point</text> in <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Mechanism &#160;A</text></para>
        </td>
