          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text2-Note">Other names for a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Ball-Joint</text> in the engineering community are: <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Rod-End</text>&#32;<text styleclass="VariableName-small">Bearing</text>, <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Heim Joint (USA),</text>&#32;<text styleclass="VariableName-small">Rose-Joint Bearing (UK)</text>.</para>
